particular religious

00:24:39.580 --> 00:24:40.990 align:middle line:90%
or spiritual tradition.

00:24:40.990 --> 00:24:41.950 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:24:41.950 --> 00:24:44.650 align:middle line:84%
>>WALLIS: They are part
