them in, no matter

00:29:38.800 --> 00:29:40.060 align:middle line:90%
what you do, to the old model.

00:29:40.060 --> 00:29:41.602 align:middle line:84%
You've got to
dismantle the old model

00:29:41.602 --> 00:29:44.920 align:middle line:84%
and build a brand new model that
can contain all the old data

00:29:44.920 --> 00:29:46.000 align:middle line:90%
and all the new data.

00:29:46.000 --> 00:29:47.890 align:middle line:84%
And we did that twice
in the 20th century

00:29:47.890 --> 00:29:53.300 align:middle line:84%
with relativity theory in 1905
and quantum mechanics in 1920.

00:29:53.300 --> 00:29:56.090 align:middle line:84%
Now, the mystics have been doing
