00:36:46.220 --> 00:36:49.760 align:middle line:84%
better remote viewing,
better precognition,

00:36:49.760 --> 00:36:51.320 align:middle line:90%
better self-healing.

00:36:51.320 --> 00:36:53.960 align:middle line:84%
And so the engineers in
the Popol Vuh stories,

00:36:53.960 --> 00:36:56.400 align:middle line:84%
think, hang on, we don't
need them this clever.

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:58.160 align:middle line:84%
Can we dial them
down a bit, so we

00:36:58.160 --> 00:37:01.670 align:middle line:84%
can manage all we want as a
workforce, for goodness' sake.

00:37:01.670 --> 00:37:03.770 align:middle line:84%
And so they have an
emergency meeting.

00:37:03.770 --> 00:37:06.440 align:middle line:84%
And they work out, the way
to dial the humans down

00:37:06.440 --> 00:37:10.220 align:middle line:84%
is to spray a vapor
over human populations

00:37:10.220 --> 00:37:13.430 align:middle line:84%
that will damage our
neurological health

00:37:13.430 --> 00:37:17.000 align:middle line:84%
and shut off these
higher capacities.

00:37:17.000 --> 00:37:19.730 align:middle line:90%
Limit our vision is the phrase.

00:37:19.730 --> 00:37:22.520 align:middle line:84%
And just to unpack
that, if you think

00:37:22.520 --> 00:37:26.870 align:middle line:84%
about how is our vision limited,
well, it's limited by surfaces.

00:37:26.870 --> 00:37:29.060 align:middle line:90%
We can't see behind things.

00:37:29.060 --> 00:37:30.960 align:middle line:90%
We can't see into things.

00:37:30.960 --> 00:37:32.333 align:middle line:90%
It's limited by time.

00:37:32.333 --> 00:37:33.500 align:middle line:90%
We can only see the present.

00:37:33.500 --> 00:37:34.490 align:middle line:90%
We can't see the past.

00:37:34.490 --> 00:37:36.140 align:middle line:90%
We can't see the future.

00:37:36.140 --> 00:37:38.000 align:middle line:90%
It's limited by distance.

00:37:38.000 --> 00:37:39.470 align:middle line:90%
We can't see beyond the horizon.

00:37:39.470 --> 00:37:41.700 align:middle line:90%
We can't see into deep space.

00:37:41.700 --> 00:37:42.980 align:middle line:90%
It's limited by frequency.

00:37:42.980 --> 00:37:46.790 align:middle line:84%
We can only see this
spectrum of radio waves.

00:37:46.790 --> 00:37:48.350 align:middle line:90%
Whereas, a dog can see this.

00:37:48.350 --> 00:37:50.270 align:middle line:90%
A cat can see this.

00:37:50.270 --> 00:37:53.090 align:middle line:84%
Take all those limits
off, all of a sudden,

00:37:53.090 --> 00:37:56.360 align:middle line:84%
you've got X-ray vision,
remote viewing, future viewing.

00:37:56.360 --> 00:38:01.340 align:middle line:84%
How do you manage and manipulate
being that intelligent?

00:38:01.340 --> 00:38:02.600 align:middle line:90%
And so, this was the story.

00:38:02.600 --> 00:38:04.430 align:middle line:90%
They sprayed a vapor.

00:38:04.430 --> 00:38:07.620 align:middle line:84%
But there's a positive
take home from the story,

00:38:07.620 --> 00:38:10.640 align:middle line:84%
and that is that
they didn't downgrade

00:38:10.640 --> 00:38:13.160 align:middle line:90%
what we are within ourselves.

00:38:13.160 --> 00:38:17.960 align:middle line:84%
They put something into the
environment to dial us down.

00:38:17.960 --> 00:38:23.060 align:middle line:84%
And the punchline of that story
is that absent of that vapor,

00:38:23.060 --> 00:38:25.550 align:middle line:84%
absent of those toxins
in the environment,

00:38:25.550 --> 00:38:29.520 align:middle line:84%
you and I start becoming
healthier, more intelligent,

00:38:29.520 --> 00:38:30.350 align:middle line:90%
more conscious.

00:38:30.350 --> 00:38:32.930 align:middle line:90%
That's our natural state.

00:38:32.930 --> 00:38:36.200 align:middle line:84%
Now, the culture that
curated that story about us

00:38:36.200 --> 00:38:37.400 align:middle line:90%
was the Mayan culture.

00:38:37.400 --> 00:38:41.510 align:middle line:84%
When the Spanish
and the Portuguese

00:38:41.510 --> 00:38:43.760 align:middle line:84%
went into central
and South America,

00:38:43.760 --> 00:38:46.940 align:middle line:84%
those were the stories
they shut down,

00:38:46.940 --> 00:38:50.420 align:middle line:84%
along with the shamanic
and mystical protocols that

00:38:50.420 --> 00:38:54.830 align:middle line:84%
existed in those cultures for
activating our higher powers.

00:38:54.830 --> 00:39:00.200 align:middle line:84%
They wanted to delete the
information and the knowledge

00:39:00.200 --> 00:39:03.530 align:middle line:84%
of how to be more conscious
and more intelligent

00:39:03.530 --> 00:39:06.620 align:middle line:84%
and replace it with
Christian orthodoxy, which

00:39:06.620 --> 00:39:09.440 align:middle line:84%
they, the conquerors,
would provide

00:39:09.440 --> 00:39:12.620 align:middle line:84%
through their churches,
their education system,

00:39:12.620 --> 00:39:14.220 align:middle line:90%
so on, and so forth.

00:39:14.220 --> 00:39:17.180 align:middle line:84%
And they created a
worldview for those living

00:39:17.180 --> 00:39:18.830 align:middle line:84%
in Central and
South America, where

00:39:18.830 --> 00:39:21.720 align:middle line:84%
you've got God at the
top of the pyramid,

00:39:21.720 --> 00:39:24.570 align:middle line:84%
along with the Kings of
Portugal and Spain and the Pope.

00:39:24.570 --> 00:39:28.260 align:middle line:84%
And then you've got the army
and the Catholic priests

00:39:28.260 --> 00:39:31.110 align:middle line:84%
in the middle, and then
the people at the bottom,

00:39:31.110 --> 00:39:33.180 align:middle line:90%
praying and obeying.

00:39:33.180 --> 00:39:37.410 align:middle line:84%
And so they've deleted this
worldview, where we all

00:39:37.410 --> 00:39:41.610 align:middle line:84%
have inter-dimensional support
and assistance, where we all

00:39:41.610 --> 00:39:43.980 align:middle line:84%
have higher cognitive
powers, and they've

00:39:43.980 --> 00:39:47.640 align:middle line:84%
replaced it with this
feudalizing structure.

00:39:47.640 --> 00:39:50.070 align:middle line:84%
And in almost every
story of colonization,

00:39:50.070 --> 00:39:54.690 align:middle line:84%
you can see that delete and
replace action going on.

00:39:54.690 --> 00:39:57.480 align:middle line:84%
And I think, in a
way, it still goes on.

00:39:57.480 --> 00:39:58.990 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yes,
thank you for that.

00:39:58.990 --> 00:40:01.770 align:middle line:84%
And you just said it,
this interdimensionality,

00:40:01.770 --> 00:40:04.500 align:middle line:84%
they were looking at one-- the
story of the vapor is looking

00:40:04.500 --> 00:40:07.320 align:middle line:84%
at one dimension of what it
is to be human rather than

00:40:07.320 --> 00:40:11.430 align:middle line:84%
our multidimensional nature and
ability to access those higher

00:40:11.430 --> 00:40:13.830 align:middle line:84%
realms of consciousness,
which were not--

00:40:13.830 --> 00:40:17.310 align:middle line:84%
I guess, they, themselves,
were not skilled at that

00:40:17.310 --> 00:40:21.660 align:middle line:84%
and thus didn't understand the
nature of multidimensionality

00:40:21.660 --> 00:40:22.930 align:middle line:90%
themselves.

00:40:22.930 --> 00:40:25.530 align:middle line:84%
>>O'LAORIE: So when I trace it,
even through the Bible itself

00:40:25.530 --> 00:40:28.950 align:middle line:84%
and into history subsequently,
I'm fascinated by it.

00:40:28.950 --> 00:40:31.540 align:middle line:84%
Firstly, I don't believe
that the God in the Bible

00:40:31.540 --> 00:40:32.340 align:middle line:90%
is the God.

00:40:32.340 --> 00:40:33.240 align:middle line:90%
I put the God on trial.

00:40:33.240 --> 00:40:35.370 align:middle line:84%
I just read a whole book where
I put God on trial against--

00:40:35.370 --> 00:40:35.460 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I love it.

00:40:35.460 --> 00:40:35.820 align:middle line:90%
I love your book.

00:40:35.820 --> 00:40:37.350 align:middle line:84%
>>O'LAORIE: --crimes
against humanity.

00:40:37.350 --> 00:40:38.808 align:middle line:84%
But one of the
things I'm seeing is

00:40:38.808 --> 00:40:41.520 align:middle line:84%
that these sky beings
of various kinds,

00:40:41.520 --> 00:40:43.500 align:middle line:84%
that when they
came here, there's

00:40:43.500 --> 00:40:45.720 align:middle line:84%
this great story of
Babel, the Tower of Babel,

00:40:45.720 --> 00:40:49.740 align:middle line:84%
where they said, let us
confuse their tongues.

00:40:49.740 --> 00:40:52.200 align:middle line:84%
Now what I hear on this
wasn't that everybody spoke

00:40:52.200 --> 00:40:55.350 align:middle line:84%
a single tongue before Babel
and that they confused us,

00:40:55.350 --> 00:40:57.305 align:middle line:84%
so they're now speaking
different languages.

00:40:57.305 --> 00:40:59.430 align:middle line:84%
My belief system is precisely
what you were saying,

00:40:59.430 --> 00:41:02.550 align:middle line:84%
Paul, is that people had
telepathic, clairvoyant,

00:41:02.550 --> 00:41:05.220 align:middle line:84%
clear scent, clear
audio capabilities.

00:41:05.220 --> 00:41:07.898 align:middle line:84%
And what they did was,
they taught them language.

00:41:07.898 --> 00:41:09.690 align:middle line:84%
So it's not that they
confused the language

00:41:09.690 --> 00:41:12.750 align:middle line:84%
by telling them reducing
all the languages to one,

00:41:12.750 --> 00:41:15.690 align:middle line:84%
but that there were telepathic
exchanges, clairvoyance,

00:41:15.690 --> 00:41:18.210 align:middle line:90%
precognition, cytokinesis.

00:41:18.210 --> 00:41:21.990 align:middle line:84%
All these powers were
resident in the creation.

00:41:21.990 --> 00:41:23.340 align:middle line:90%
And they shut them all off.

00:41:23.340 --> 00:41:24.965 align:middle line:84%
And now, they're
going to have to focus

00:41:24.965 --> 00:41:27.060 align:middle line:90%
on the verbalization of ideas.

00:41:27.060 --> 00:41:29.400 align:middle line:84%
And as soon as you try to
put thoughts into word,

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:32.070 align:middle line:84%
words are very,
very leaky vessels.

00:41:32.070 --> 00:41:36.480 align:middle line:84%
If you look at any piece of
artwork, even for 10 seconds,

00:41:36.480 --> 00:41:38.550 align:middle line:84%
and you try to
describe it, it's going

00:41:38.550 --> 00:41:41.370 align:middle line:84%
to take you a million words
to describe what you've

00:41:41.370 --> 00:41:43.350 align:middle line:90%
just witnessed and taken it.

00:41:43.350 --> 00:41:45.697 align:middle line:84%
And so, words can't
do justice to it.

00:41:45.697 --> 00:41:47.280 align:middle line:84%
So you reduce it
down to one language.

00:41:47.280 --> 00:41:49.863 align:middle line:84%
Now, over time, it's spread
into many, many languages.

00:41:49.863 --> 00:41:52.030 align:middle line:84%
Now, historically, I think
what we've done with that

00:41:52.030 --> 00:41:55.740 align:middle line:84%
and we realized that
every language creates

00:41:55.740 --> 00:41:58.200 align:middle line:84%
a mindset, which
creates a culture,

00:41:58.200 --> 00:42:00.510 align:middle line:84%
and it articulates
in story form.

00:42:00.510 --> 00:42:03.510 align:middle line:84%
And stories become the
archived wisdom of the culture.

00:42:03.510 --> 00:42:06.610 align:middle line:84%
Now, when the colonials
move in, what do they do?

00:42:06.610 --> 00:42:09.510 align:middle line:84%
The first thing is they try
to destroy the language.

00:42:09.510 --> 00:42:12.190 align:middle line:84%
By the beginning of
the 20th century,

00:42:12.190 --> 00:42:14.160 align:middle line:84%
there were 7,000
languages on planet Earth.

00:42:14.160 --> 00:42:15.690 align:middle line:84%
By the end of that
century, there

00:42:15.690 --> 00:42:17.100 align:middle line:90%
were 5,000 languages left.

00:42:17.100 --> 00:42:20.820 align:middle line:84%
So there were 7,000
different mindsets trying

00:42:20.820 --> 00:42:22.450 align:middle line:90%
to grasp the human experience.

00:42:22.450 --> 00:42:25.980 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you shut down a
language, what you're doing is

00:42:25.980 --> 00:42:27.570 align:middle line:84%
you're shutting
down the stories.

00:42:27.570 --> 00:42:29.037 align:middle line:84%
You shut down the
stories, you're

00:42:29.037 --> 00:42:30.120 align:middle line:90%
shutting down the culture.

00:42:30.120 --> 00:42:33.090 align:middle line:84%
You shut down the culture,
you're selling the cosmology.

00:42:33.090 --> 00:42:35.458 align:middle line:84%
And so you've left people
without a cosmology.

00:42:35.458 --> 00:42:37.500 align:middle line:84%
I know you come in, you
say, here's the language.

00:42:37.500 --> 00:42:39.930 align:middle line:84%
Here's the culture, and
here's the cosmology.

00:42:39.930 --> 00:42:42.030 align:middle line:84%
And it has to do
with our technology,

00:42:42.030 --> 00:42:44.940 align:middle line:84%
and there's a stratification, as
Paul mentioned so beautifully,

00:42:44.940 --> 00:42:47.440 align:middle line:84%
a hierarchical system,
a secular version of it,

00:42:47.440 --> 00:42:48.690 align:middle line:90%
and a religious version of it.

00:42:48.690 --> 00:42:51.510 align:middle line:84%
And now, you've got the peons
at the bottom with no stories

00:42:51.510 --> 00:42:55.170 align:middle line:84%
to tell, no cosmology,
no culture, no language,

00:42:55.170 --> 00:42:56.670 align:middle line:90%
except that of the colonialist.

00:42:56.670 --> 00:42:58.830 align:middle line:90%
And now, we're powerless.

00:42:58.830 --> 00:43:02.580 align:middle line:84%
And that's been actively--
throughout human history, it's

00:43:02.580 --> 00:43:05.970 align:middle line:84%
been actively, including our
own, time's being promoted.

00:43:05.970 --> 00:43:08.850 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Now, this is what
I mentioned a moment ago,

00:43:08.850 --> 00:43:10.920 align:middle line:84%
that some of the other
offers, my friend, Michael

00:43:10.920 --> 00:43:13.380 align:middle line:84%
Hollinger and others
refer to, as reducing us

00:43:13.380 --> 00:43:14.760 align:middle line:90%
to a slave species.

00:43:14.760 --> 00:43:17.123 align:middle line:84%
Now when I even
say those words--

00:43:17.123 --> 00:43:19.290 align:middle line:84%
and we're just going to
wrap it up on this question.

