00:45:02.830 --> 00:45:04.150 align:middle line:90%
That was part of our story.

00:45:04.150 --> 00:45:06.460 align:middle line:84%
I think we have
experienced colonization

00:45:06.460 --> 00:45:08.200 align:middle line:90%
